Class TreeStage_MinDepth

  • java.lang.Object
    • tree.TreeStage
      • tree.TreeStage_MinDepth
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable

    public class TreeStage_MinDepth
extends TreeStage
    Searches until we meet a minimum depth requirement in all branches sort of like a BFS. This might never terminate with some greedy searches so be careful.
    Author:
    matt
